{
  "stem": "11801.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were hundreds of us as far as I-- at least that's the way I remember it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train trip [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was very difficult, because all of a sudden I realized that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that my mother was not with us and that my father was not with us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also realized that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my brother was my responsibility, and I felt very strongly about taking care of my brother-- I always have all my life-- and that the future was very unknown.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was only eight years old, but I, I did realize that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew I was leaving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew exactly what was happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe my parents did talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I certainly learned about it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, I experienced enough of it to, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to be very frightened and to be very hurt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- there was one incident that I'll never forget when-- the way I remember it, a child-- I was outside, and a child threw something at me, either a stone or a piece of glass.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it hit me in the arm, and I started to bleed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember bleeding profusely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother said I didn't, but, you know, maybe as a child that's the way I remember it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after that, I, I refused to go and play outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We played outside a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't have much of a garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't-- you know, it was a little courtyard in the back, but basically the children played on street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after that, I, I refused to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I would look out of the window and watch other children, but I, myself, was much too afraid and too, too upset with that experience.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
